Grails plugin for Facebook Authentication, as extension to Grails Spring Security Core plugin.

h1. Introduction

Sources: [https://github.com/splix/grails-spring-security-facebook|https://github.com/splix/grails-spring-security-facebook]

h2. Requirements:
 * grails 2.0+
 * spring-security-core plugin 1.2.7.2

h2. Examples:

  * [https://github.com/splix/grails-facebook-authentication-example|https://github.com/splix/grails-facebook-authentication-example] - Example app (based on Grails 2.1.1)

h2. Support

 * if you found a bug - please submit it into [GitHub Issues|https://github.com/splix/grails-spring-security-facebook/issues]